    "html": "<DOCUMENT>\n<TYPE>EX-99.1\n<SEQUENCE>2\n<FILENAME>ex991.htm\n<DESCRIPTION>NEWS RELEASE DATED MAY 9, 2019\n<TEXT>\n<HTML>\n<HEAD>\n     <TITLE></TITLE>\n</HEAD>\n<BODY STYLE=\"font: 10pt Times New Roman, Times, Serif\">\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: right\"><FONT STYLE=\"font: 8pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif\"><B>Exhibit 99.1</B></FONT></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: right\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: right\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: right\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: right\"></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"margin: 0; text-align: left\"><IMG SRC=\"image_001.jpg\" ALT=\"\" STYLE=\"width: 355px; height: 69px\"></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\"></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\"></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\"></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\"></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: bold 14pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-right: 0; margin-left: 0\">Wheaton Precious Metals Announces Election\nof Directors and Approval of Special Matters</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 12pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-right: 0; margin-left: 0\">TSX: WPM<BR>\nNYSE: WPM</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 12pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin-right: 0; margin-left: 0\">VANCOUVER, May 9, 2019 /CNW/ - Wheaton Precious\nMetals&trade; Corp. (&quot;Wheaton&quot; or the &quot;Company&quot;) announces that the nominees listed below were elected as directors\nof Wheaton at the 2019 Annual and Special Meeting of Shareholders. Detailed results of the vote for directors of the Company held\nat the Annual and Special Meeting of Shareholders earlier today are shown below:</P>\n\n<TABLE CELLSPACING=\"0\" CELLPADDING=\"0\" STYLE=\"width: 100%; font: 7.5pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; border-collapse: collapse\">\n<TR>\n    <TD STYLE=\"white-space: nowrap; border: Black 1pt solid; padding-left: 6pt\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\"><B>Nominee</B></FONT></TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"white-space: nowrap; vertical-align: bottom; border-top: black 1pt solid; border-right: black 1pt solid; border-bottom: black 1pt solid; padding-right: 6pt; padding-left: 6pt; text-align: center\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\"><B>Votes For</B></FONT></TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"white-space: nowrap; vertical-align: bottom; border-top: black 1pt solid; border-right: black 1pt solid; border-bottom: black 1pt solid; padding-right: 6pt; padding-left: 6pt; text-align: center\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\"><B>% For</B></FONT></TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"white-space: nowrap; vertical-align: bottom; border-top: black 1pt solid; border-right: black 1pt solid; border-bottom: black 1pt solid; padding-right: 6pt; padding-left: 6pt; text-align: center\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\"><B>Votes </B></FONT><BR>\n<FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\"><B>Withheld</B></FONT></TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"white-space: nowrap; vertical-align: bottom; border-top: black 1pt solid; border-right: black 1pt solid; border-bottom: black 1pt solid; padding-right: 6pt; padding-left: 6pt; text-align: center\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\"><B>% Withheld</B></FONT></TD></TR>\n<TR STYLE=\"vertical-align: bottom\">\n    <TD STYLE=\"white-space: nowrap; border-right: black 1pt solid; border-bottom: black 1pt solid; border-left: black 1pt solid; padding-right: 6pt; padding-left: 6pt\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\">George L. Brack</FONT></TD>\n    <TD STYLE=\"white-space: nowrap; bord